				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$X_0$$\end{document}, depending on pseudorapidity; the detector material description is adjusted accordingly. The MVA calibration is optimised with the improved simulation, and the calorimeter absolute energy scale is determined using electron pairs from Z\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
